        <h1 class="text-center" id="whatislincH1" style="color:white">What is LINC?</h1>
        <p id="what-is-linc" class="lead lead-large lead-small text-center">The Lion Identification Network of Collaborators (LINC) is an open source platform conceived to change the base methodology of how lion research can be enacted across fragmented geographies and diverse conservation efforts. LINC uses a custom web application, consisting of a collaborative database combined with innovative AI search and identification capabilities, allowing the consolidation and retrieval of lion data for conservationists, researchers and government wildlife management.
        </p>
