        <h2><strong>COMMUNITY GENERATED DATABASE</strong></h2>
        <p>Researchers across organizations can record, organize and share lion data generating a more complete understanding of the metapopulation dynamics.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 col-sm-8 col-md-4 col-lg-3 m-sm-auto pt-5 pt-md-0 mt-lg-0">
        <img alt="image" class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lynn-de-souza/image/upload/v1548347093/LINC%20website/Home/CompIcon.png">
        <h2><strong>EASY TO USE WEBSITE</strong></h2>
        <p>The user interface is designed to help researchers access and utilize data quickly and efficiently, leading the paradigm shift away from paper records and fragmented datapools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 col-sm-8 col-md-4 col-lg-3 m-sm-auto ml-md-auto mr-md-0 pt-5 pt-md-0">
        <img alt="image" class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lynn-de-souza/image/upload/v1548347094/LINC%20website/Home/Tick_1.png">
          <h2><strong>LION RECOGNITION SOFTWARE</strong></h2>
          <p>AI assisted facial and whisker recognition algorithms allow users to compare photographs of unknown lions to an expansive database of individuals, helping to identify lions who move beyond an organizationsâ€™ study areas.</p>
